OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F384A1780513862
OL,3,CGuernsey's #45 million surplus masks
OL,4,Cunderlying deficit
OL,6,FStates of Guernsey's day-to-day
OL,7,Ffinances are operating at a surplus of
OL,8,F#45 million, according to new figures.
OL,10,FIt marks a dramatic shift from the #44
OL,11,Fmillion deficit the year before,
OL,12,Faccording to the States Accounts
OL,13,Freleased on Tuesday 2 June.
OL,15,FHowever, the report also cautioned
OL,16,Fthat "much of the improvement reflects
OL,17,Fone-off items rather than a sustained
OL,18,Fimprovement in underlying finances",
OL,19,Fand that there is still an underlying
OL,20,Ffunding gap of around #50 million.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
